I created this map based off of there maps that I have created for regular counter strike some time ago so don’t post about improper credit or credit theft  as I’m the creator of these maps. This  map was created in the summer and will be my last game play orientated map that I add to this web site. I hope you enjoy it has much has the regulars on my server do If you would like to know the secrets of the map you will have to donate me 100 points and ill tell you.
